er to solve puzzles, share strategies, and escape the deadly mazes. Can you survive the endless corridors and unravel the mystery within Creepy Apes? Or will you become their next victim?", "short_description": "Creepy Apes is a terrifying VR horror game set within a labyrinth of dark, twisted mazes inhabited by horrifying, mutated apes. Navigate through a series of increasingly complex mazes, from eerie industrial settings to shadowy underground tunnels, using intuitive arm movements to climb, push, and escape the lurking danger. Collect cosmetics to customize your character and join friends in multiplayer mode, where you can talk, strategize, and survive together. Each maze is packed with scary AI's"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://docs.google.com/document/d/1XLKOKPFbOgT3aZvCLbQy_wqzyS-iHznuBQOqUN49A74/edit?usp=sharing", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Snowzy VR", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://matthewcrandon023.wixsite.com/creepy-apes", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "411892083130028"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER"], "id": "7329545707148787"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1044708573902873"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1044708573902873"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1726066260, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1044708573902873"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": 